text: Romário Xolo Maridueña (; born June 9, 2001) is an American actor. He is best known for his role as Miguel Diaz in the Netflix series Cobra Kai, and as Victor Graham in the TV series Parenthood. He will play Jaime Reyes / Blue Beetle in the future Blue Beetle DC Extended Universe movie. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:American child actors
